<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l5">vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> . vvıe Jm der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> etwıeuıl ſchuldıg ſey vnd 
<add><ab facs="#facs_164_line_1586276426492_326">Jn </ab></add> auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_164_r1l6"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſecʒt</expan> hab . des er von Jm niht <expan>bekome<ex>n</ex></expan> künn . vvıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır </ab>
